description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 9, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 45, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 3 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [45 Votes, Common]
